question.title: Can't run JavaFX in Intellij Idea
question.body:
I create a JavaFx project using IntelliJ following the doc: https://openjfx.io/openjfx-docs/, but the sample file HelloApplication.java (along with other files) is not runnable no matter what I tried. Dont know what should I do about it Screenshot

I watched some tutorial videos about JavaFx set up but nobody encouter the same situation like me, at least all their sample code can run
